snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Mercuris' Chest Demo Announcement
snippet.description:
The Legend of Zelda: Mercuris’ Chest is the next game by the team behind the Solarus engine.
Check out the demo, available on April 1st 2023… as announced 21 years ago: https://www.solarus-games.org/zmc

Learn more about our projects on: https://www.solarus-games.org
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/yYHjJHt

Music by Stringer Bell: https://pixabay.com/fr/users/stringer_bell-27113883

#solarus #demo #ReleaseDate #zelda #nintendo #TheLegendOfZelda
